# Knowledge Index Platform context

This repo is a **standalone index microservice** (Features 001–002 only).

## Gates (replace any `domain:*` references)

- **No** `domain:extract`, `domain:check`, or `domain.graph.yaml` — not installed here.
- Use constitution Quality Gates: `npm test`, `npm run validate`, CLI dry-runs.
